Project Overview:

This project provides a clean and structured API layer to interact with Microsoft SharePoint using Microsoft Graph.
It supports authentication, site management, list management, list items operations, and drive/file operations.

To run the project:

pdm start

Documentation Guide:

Navigate to the docs/ directory for complete API and internal module documentation.

